name: Phoenix diaries - spirals of countless returns
description:
Combination of analog and digital drawing/illustration. 
Part of the Feathered Tales collection within the Hybrid Mythologies universe. This collection arose gradually as I was drawing, painting, watching and reading about birds that I have a tremendous fascination of. Oftentimes I depict birds from mixing mythologies or legends or representing them in a symbolic and archetypical way. This piece is about cycles of transformation symbolized by Phoenix - life, death, rebirth continually in a cycle.
